{"tid":1364424,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【遍地開花】香港寬頻員工致香港人","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:46:46.000Z","uid":289271,"like":333,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"af2662048bc84e7bec1ad79b442b3a1f3718eb61","tid":1364424,"uid":289271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"致 香港人︰<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群微不足道的香港寬頻員工。雖然我們不是當權者下的公僕，更遑論是致力「服務市民」的執法者，但出於一片熱愛香港的丹心，我們不願被噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n「成就香港更美好家園」是公司一直矢志達成的使命。然而，昨天其中一位員工Kenji Lam卻就7月21日元朗襲擊一事發表了「大快人心」之言論，令人極度震驚及心寒。身為香港人，我們對此予以強烈讉責，雖說基本法賦以港人不可褫奪的言論自由，但其言論泯滅人性，人神共憤，恥與為伍！再者，該名員工同為香港寬頻持股管理人之一（注︰即Co-Owner，意指香港寬頻股東），位高權重更應慎言其行，我們在此要求Kenji Lam必須撤回言論並立即向港人，尤其是元朗受襲之受傷者公開致歉，否則我們將與一眾香港人同行，追究到底，誓不罷休！<br />\n<br />\n同時，我們亦與絕大部分港人一樣，心裡無比恐懼卻不憤向暴政低頭而無數次站上街頭。然而，對於連埸示威活動，政府卻選擇以傲慢態度對待，更縱容警察濫用暴力及選擇性執法，更令人心寒的是於元朗襲擊一事，政府竟容許不法之徒逃之夭夭，讓我們終日活於白色恐怖之下。示威活動亦隨民怨持續升溫，社會日趨撕裂，若執政者仍選擇漠視人民聲音，殘局將會一發不可收拾。<br />\n<br />\n我們在此嚴厲要求政府正面回應市民五大訴求，及Kenji Lam必須撤回其無恥言論並公開致歉，決一不可！<br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撒回暴動定性<br />\n3. 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 追究警隊濫暴<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n6. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Kenji Lam撤回其「大快人心」言論並公開致歉</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「不在沉默中爆發 就在沉默中滅亡」&mdash; 魯迅<br />\n<br />\n一群寧做雞蛋亦不做高牆的香港寬頻員工 敬上<br />\n<br />\n（以上言論與公司及Kenji Lam立場完全無關）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/cP5s9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2FcP5s9C.jpg&h=fdc92186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/eGt7lC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2FeGt7lC.jpg&h=9dfe9fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/IRg9zE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2FIRg9zE.jpg&h=10e95703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/It9P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2FIt9P0v.jpg&h=a0212d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/LVRur2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2FLVRur2.jpg&h=ce36e58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/WhXRTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2FWhXRTL.jpg&h=67ff214b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/oQfVP2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2FoQfVP2.jpg&h=24c40152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">追究黑警冇警告下開36鎗\n\n727 元朗見\n\n光復香港 時代革命</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b75cdf21318a111e76386ead571c8410f4fd726f","tid":1364424,"uid":56698,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"咁濕鳩張張都寫住Talent嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b844516be4734f7d3eba67d29cd429d7463097a","tid":1364424,"uid":35556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519f2d8c0ca0d6cfae592a3bd0bdbe77f03965b4","tid":1364424,"uid":236780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"大快人心"},{"pid":"618a6a1981ebb2acee0a5132a75380a05a8534d2","tid":1364424,"uid":241297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遍地開花！</span></span>"},{"pid":"78105b98b17bd1bdefb87deb98a6610ca25d9ffd","tid":1364424,"uid":30541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"繼續開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fba22251ff455ba389aa4455